# Book Lovers — Multipage Site

Multipage website (Home, African Literature, Thrillers, Contact).
Built with HTML5, CSS, and a JS file for interactivity.

## Structure
- index.html — Home
- african.html — African Literature
- thrillers.html — Thriller authors
- contact.html — Contact form with validation
- css/styles.css — Styling and responsive rules
- js/script.js — Nav toggle + form validation + utilities

## How to preview locally
1. Open `index.html` in a browser (or open the folder in VS Code and use Live Server).
2. Navigate pages through the top menu.

